# Frontend performance

- Import MUI components from their direct paths (`@mui/material/Button`), not barrel imports.
- Use `next/image` for all recipe photos.
- Paginate feeds; never fetch unbounded recipe lists.
- Lazy-load heavy screens (create recipe, profile edit) with `next/dynamic`.
